{
  "stem": "3690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hitchhiked, and I walked, and I was hiding out in every way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally I got to Budapest by hitchhiking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you call, farmers, used to go with horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to offer them help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I could help him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you want me, can I go in with you to town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they carry their produce into Budapest to sell their produce, these farmers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, OK, if you're going to help me, you can come with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can follow the wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you get too tired, you can sit on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, they wouldn't let you to go on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once you get friendly with them and you got too tired, so they let you sit on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You got into it town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I says to the man, I'm going to look around and I'll be back to help you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So of course you didn't have the mind to come back and help him, but you had to see what you can do for yourself because you were afraid he will give you away or what happened, because he didn't know you, you don't know him.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he didn't ask much questions because you didn't even-- you didn't offer any voluntary, you know-- you didn't want to tell him who you are or what you come from-- where you come from.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started looking around and asking people if there is any Jewish synagogue still open or any, any temples or anything where I can go and inquire about something what I can do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one woman told me, yes, there is somewhere in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], somewhere, it's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
